long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension brings the chilling presence of the Grim Reaper to your browser. With a spectral figure draped in dark robes, the Reaper’s haunting presence fills the screen, enhanced by dynamic, atmospheric effects that add a supernatural edge to your new tab.

Features:
⚰️ Spooky live wallpaper of the Grim Reaper in a haunting style.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to keep track of your time.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Let the Grim Reaper’s haunting presence guide your browsing experience with an air of mystery every time you open a new tab.
